Definition: deciduous roundheaded Asiatic tree widely grown in mild climates as an ornamental for its heart-shaped leaves and fragrant yellow-green flowers followed by hanging clusters of fleshy orange-red berries
Synonyms: Idesia_polycarpa, tree, genus_Idesia, m, deciduous, roundheaded, Asiatic, widely, grown, in, mild, climates, as, an, ornamental, for, its, heart-shaped, leaves, and, fragrant, yellow-green, flowers, followed, by, hanging, clusters, of, fleshy, orange-red, berries
Category: noun.plant
